# Function to delete commmon words
def remove_stopwords(text):
    return " ".join([word for word in str(text).split() 
                     if word not in stop_words])
In [53]:
# Function to keep only alphabet and digits; remove punctuations and special chars.
def keep_alnum(text):
    return " ".join([word for word in str(text).split() 
                     if word.isalnum()])
In [77]:
# Function to remove digits
def remove_digit(text):
    return " ".join([word for word in str(text).split() 
                     if not word.isdigit()])

Prepossessing¶

In [81]:
# Clean the dataset
des_cleaned = description.apply( lambda doc: doc.strip().lower())\
.apply(lambda doc: remove_stopwords(doc))\
.apply(lambda doc: keep_alnum(doc))\
.apply(lambda doc: remove_digit(doc))
In [82]:
des_cleaned.to_csv('cleaned_description.csv')

                embedding_model='universal-sentence-encoder')

The used car trading company are more likely to appear than some of the most popular description terms like ford, suv, bmw. It appears that a lot of the sellers are from used car company.¶
